Dialogue: 0,0:00:-01.00,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future --\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright,\Nbut I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really\Nneed everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Alabasta's Hero and\Na Ballerina on the Ship!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:02:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of our way! Out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... Crocodile-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As always, he came for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.07,0:02:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it's the Crocodile,\None of the Seven Warlords...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, ignorant people!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just came to get that pirate's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so wonderful...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you always say,\Nbut you always save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray for Crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.29,0:03:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alabasta's Guardian Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King of the desert! Crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.07,0:03:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, call me what you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, pirates, don't cause\Na ruckus in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.71,0:03:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey, hey!\NAren't you underestimating us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.15,0:03:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning to take\Non all of us by yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the government's dog,\None who sold his soul to authority!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are,\Nacting like a hero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who don't wanna die,\Nlay down on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he an idiot or what?!\NHe's a perfect target for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.69,0:03:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him! The money and\Nvaluables in this town are ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:04:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what the famous\NSeven Warlords are like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.26,0:04:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:05:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a pirate on a\Ndifferent level, you pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile! Crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.81,0:05:43.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Alubarna Palace, Alabasta Kingdom"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was one step ahead again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the time we got to Nanohana,\Nit was already...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.02,0:05:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, it's fine as long\Nas the citizens are okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:55.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"King of Alabasta, Nefertari Cobra"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:06:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He does a lot for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake.\NThis ship is heading to Alabasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be there soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.61,0:06:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you looking away?\NLook me in the eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, seriously... I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did enough food for 8 people,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which I carefully divided so that\Nit'd last until we get to Alabasta,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,disappear during the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fighting, it's pointless!\NYou've got a horrible poker face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burp...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you have something\Naround your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Shoot! Food crumbs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:07:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, it was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh, Nami-san...\NYou saw it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The large rat trap\Nis no longer good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please buy a lockable refrigerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think about it... since it\Ncan be a life or death issue...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.34,0:07:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...! We'd better catch\Nsomething for Sanji-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, any luck fishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel good...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, I can't take my eyes\Noff these guys for a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... I'm starving...\NThe fish aren't biting at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! It's your fault!\NIt's because you even ate the bait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't have bait,\Nthe fish won't bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ate it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I only ate the\Nstuff on the bait box cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san. Usopp-san.\NHave you caught anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karoo! Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we can\Ncatch a shark or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna catch a Sea King.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you two... doing to Karoo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.31,0:08:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's cotton candy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san, there's a problem!\NCome right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:09:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... don't worry.\NIt's nothing. It's just steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.21,0:09:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Steam is coming up from the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's a hot spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an area where magma is produced.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.59,0:09:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an undersea volcano\Nunderneath that area.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.49,0:09:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A volcano even though it's undersea?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.06,0:09:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. There're more undersea\Nvolcanoes than above ground ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.23,0:09:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really care...\Nsince it's not food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the volcano like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a new island will be born here over\Nthousands or tens of thousands of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cool, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tens of thousands of years...\NI wonder if I can live that long...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're a human. So you should\Ntry dying sometime before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.38,0:09:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you caught anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh hey, Sanji. I'm hungry.\NCook something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys're hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go search the storage thoroughly\Nto see if there's anything left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:10:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! It smells of sulfur!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't see anything!\NThere's steam everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bear with it. We should\Nbe through it soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 2, Bon Clay-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's smoke at 12 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter! Cut through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, unless we take care\Nof Mr. 3, I'll be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir! We're going in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this foggy thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't see ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got through!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Mr. 2, Bon Clay-sama is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look for him in the cabins!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.72,0:10:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 2, Bon Clay-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:11:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I jump on the duck\Nthat I suddenly came across?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is he a human?\N--Dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?! Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't swim--!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.98,0:11:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd die...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'm really swanny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that I was saved by\Npirates who are total strangers...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forget your\Nkindness for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, may I have a cup of warm soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the ones who're hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.57,0:12:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey you! What a cutie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my type!\NI wanna eat you! Smooch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.97,0:12:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a weirdo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you can't swim, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I ate a devil fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? What kind of fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... since there's no need to rush\Nuntil my ship comes to pick me up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In lieu of entertainment,\NI'll show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just told you that\Nthis is entertainment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.27,0:12:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprised?! Surprised?! Surprised?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I touch my face with my left hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?! I'm back to myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the power of the\NClone Clone Fruit I ate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.19,0:13:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The body was also the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A... Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, for that matter,\NI don't have to knock you down...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I have to do is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,touch faces with my right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,mimic anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bodies, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.92,0:13:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... sorry, but I can't\Nshow any more of my power...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing! Do it more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh... Well... if you insist...\NI guess I'll show more...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah! Show it! Show it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Gee, he's actually into it!\N--Yeah! Show it! Show it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Gee, he's actually into it!\N--We wanna see! We wanna see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Well then, I guess I'll show...\N--We wanna see! We wanna see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:14:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, I'm equipped\Nwith a memory feature!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spin! Spin! Spin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spin! Spin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.70,0:14:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how was my secret talent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.14,0:14:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I usually never show it to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Gimme a break! Gimme a break!\N--Amazing! Amazing! He's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Amazing! He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already time to say goodbye...?\NWhat a shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Journeys are always\Naccompanied by farewells..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't ever forget this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.24,0:15:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friendship... has nothing to do with\Nhow long we've known each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir! Mr. 2, Bon Clay-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 2?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.99,0:15:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he is... Mr. 2, Bon Clay...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.03,0:15:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi! You didn't know his face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I've never met Mr. 2\Nand Mr. 1 as well as his partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know their powers, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,though I've heard of rumors...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 2 is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.62,0:15:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a ballerina with a large frame...\Nwho talks like a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He always wears a swan coat that\Nhas "Bon Clay" on the back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've noticed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Vivi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.36,0:16:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among the faces that he\Nshowed from his past memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from his memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw my father's face...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the face of Alabasta's King,\NNefertari Cobra...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If, for example,\Nyou could mimic a king...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.31,0:16:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd be able to do\Nquite bad things, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We let a troublesome\Nguy slip away, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he's our enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's certainly quite a problem\Nif he's on our enemy's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.29,0:16:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he realizes that we're his enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he transforms into one of us\Nusing his memory from earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we won't be able to\Ntrust our own friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.18,0:16:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that his opinion\Ndoesn't have any basis,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's right about us not\Nhaving to be scared of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should consider ourselves lucky\Nthat we got to see him now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.09,0:16:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because we can figure\Nout counter-measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.86,0:17:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Mr. 2, Bon Clay-sama is in a\Nvery good mood for some reason.\N--Un, deux, trios! How do you say 4?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a small friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something came out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sea monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first meal in 4 days!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on the right track.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we get there pretty soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.63,0:17:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! It backed away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have the ship go back! Go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-W-W-W-We can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Don't let it get away!\NCapture it without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I cook you, cat monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:18:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi! You jerk! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W... Why... Vivi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.19,0:18:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Cats are a\Nsacred animal in Alabasta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've told us sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There sure are many kinds\Nof creatures in the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being scared of things like that...\NYou've still got a long way to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.37,0:18:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you a story about when I\Nbravely fought Sea Kings in the Calm Belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fought Sea Kings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big ones! They were this big!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O... Our food got away...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry. You'll be\Nable to stuff yourself soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! What cat will appear this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi! The wind and weather\Nseem to be becoming stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've entered Alabasta's climate area.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Sea Cat appearing is also the proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what we see behind us...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.91,0:19:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is probably also proof\Nof Alabasta being close...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're so many ships!\NWhen did that happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...! They all have\Nthe Baroque Works' symbol!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its employees have started gathering...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably Billions...\Nthe Officer Agents' subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that our\Nenemy is at least 200...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, they are the\N200 elites of Baroque Works...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.34,0:19:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're far from those bounty\Nhunters in Whisky Peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we fire at them while we can?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get on it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quicker if we go\Nthere and beat them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait! We have to eat first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Don't bother. They're small fries.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.63,0:19:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we lose our real target, that'll be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:20:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're only 8 of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, tie it tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our enemy this time\Nhas too many mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we check this, we don't\Nhave to doubt our friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that Clone Clone Fruit guy really\Nbecome so similar when he transforms?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've no idea! It's not "similar."\NIt's "the same"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad! You should've seen it.\NWe even danced with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in a male ballerina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing someone like that\Nis among our enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.01,0:20:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can't carelessly act alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.91,0:20:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.85,0:20:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... Do what you can do.\NYou don't have to do anything more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to run away from\Nthe enemy you can't defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you telling that to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I can do, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:20:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see the island now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop at the town called Nanohana.\NWe have to hide the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! At any rate,\Nno matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this thing on our left arm is\Nthe sign of our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, we'll land!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To a restaurant! Oh, and to Alabasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.49,0:21:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a side note?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy this time is an\Nassassination gang, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.79,0:21:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.13,0:21:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful about acting\Non instinct, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I got it.\NYeah! That's right! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.41,0:21:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even this sleepless town\Nhas dozed off for now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.72,0:22:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From today forth,\Nsomething's going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.83,0:22:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I can start fresh,\Nsince I'm not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.11,0:22:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just by having you by my side,\NI feel I can become strong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.59,0:22:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how far I can go,\Ntowards the place that leads to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.03,0:22:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off in the distance it shines,\Nencompassing the world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.38,0:22:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food! Food! Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.92,0:22:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Alabasta!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a town full of life!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.82,0:23:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... quite hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.02,0:23:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The town still seems peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When will the riot actually occur...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.79,0:23:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to stop it, right, Vivi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.53,0:23:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes.\N--Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.73,0:23:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.20,0:23:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Off to the Desert Kingdom! The Rain-\NSummoning Powder and the Rebel Army"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
